videos.description: East Tennessee State's Jermaine Long hits David Burrell on a fast break and Burrell throws it down.
videos.headline: Long lobs an alley-oop to Burrell from near half court

videos.description: Sacha Killeya-Jones gets the steal and Quade Green hits the open shot to get the Wildcats within 3.
videos.headline: Green knocks down jumper to cut lead to 3

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander gets the steal, drives to the hoop and dumps it off to Hamidou Diallo for Kentucky's first lead of the night at 26-25.
videos.headline: Fast break gives Kentucky first lead

videos.description: P.J. Washington skies for the follow-up dunk over a defender.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Washington with a forceful follow

videos.description: Kevin Knox takes it the length of the court and finishes with a smooth floater.
videos.headline: Knox goes coast-to-coast

videos.description: Quade Green tosses up a pass to Kevin Knox who makes an acrobatic finish off the glass and draws a flagrant foul in the process.
videos.headline: Green lobs it to Knox who lays in the and-1 for Kentucky

videos.description: Sacha Killeya-Jones grabs the put back and throws it down to extend Kentucky's lead.
videos.headline: Killeya-Jones cleans up the trash for Wildcats
